11:
How many times do I gotta tell you?
Look. Me. In. The. Eyes!
22: All right, that's enough for today.
25:
If you can't see your opponent's
eyes, how're you supposed to find
the right moment to pounce?
26:
Plus, I can see you shakin' the whole
time, hesitatin'. Hits that should land,
don't.
31:
I'm s-sorry... I had you go through all
this trouble to help me, but I still
can't do anything right...
36: You still can't look him in the eyes?
39:
No... Maybe this training isn't very
effective after all.
43:
My master DID say that I'd only
overcome this by testing myself in
real combat.
47:
Real combat? Who do you expect
would just be willin' to fight you at
the drop of a hat?
51:
Wait, there might actually be people
willing to do that...
58:
Yeah, that's what I was thinkin'.
They're likely to just go chargin' in on
their own against her.
60:
They might be pretty good sparrin'
partners.
70:
Huh? You were JUST talking about
how keen you were to fight.
75:
B-but... owww, my stomach hurts all
of a sudden!
79:
Dealin' with you is provin' to be quite
the hassle...
81:
Melmyna. You ARE strong. There's
zero doubt about that. Seein' you
move, that much is clear.
84:
How long are you gonna go 'round
pretendin' to be weak? I'm tired of
seein' it.
101:
Leave it to me! I'll look them in the
eyes and fight! This time I'll do it.
106: You go out there and kick some ass!
113:
Yar, if you care for your life, you'll be
handing all that sweet cargo over to
me!
116:
Look them in the eyes... Look them in
the eyes...
120:
What's this? A girl? Are YOU
supposed to be our opponent?
131: I did it?! I can't believe it—I did it!
133:
Nimbus, Nimbus, did you see? I...
actually looked at him before I took
him out!
138: Well she seems proud of herself.
144: Hahaha, yes, yes, just like that!
153:
Uh, Mel, are you sure you're not
overdoin' it there?
158:
No problem! I'm looking them in the
eyes, after all!
162: I guess we're finished! That was fast...
164:
I finally managed to stare them
down, so I was hoping it would last a
little bit longer...
168: But they all went and surrendered!
171:
Oh well. I'll just have to look forward
to my next battle!
175:
We... might have unleashed
something dangerous here, huh.
180:
None of my business. I don't wanna
think about it.
184:
Nimbus, you're the one who taught
her to do this!
189: Not my monkey, not my circus!
